            </div>

            <h5><a href="/card/LL05-052/">LL05-052 "Hanamaru Kunikida"</a></h5>
            <div class="seealso">
                See also: <a href="/faq/general#skill_order_multiple_skills">What if a Member card has two or more
                    Skills?</a>
            </div>
            <div class="question" id="052_rush">
                If this card
                is <%- skillFormat("⟪ENTER⟫ed using a [RUSH], can I use it's own [RUSH] in addition to it's [On Entry]") %>
                Skill?
            </div>
            <div class="answer">
                No. You can only use
                one <%- skillFormat("[RUSH] per turn, so you cannot use this card's [RUSH]") %>.
            </div>
            <div class="question" id="052_icon">
                Using this
                card's <%- skillFormat("[On Entry] Skill, I ⟪ENTER⟫ed another <a href=\"/card/LL05-052/\">LL05-052 \"Hanamaru Kunikida\"</a>. Does this count as being ⟪ENTER⟫ed using [RUSH]") %>
                ?
            </div>
            <div class="answer">
                No. The Skill requires this card to have
                been <%- skillFormat("⟪ENTER⟫ed as the direct result of a [RUSH]. It does not depend on whether the card you used to ⟪ENTER⟫ this card has a [RUSH]") %>
                icon or not.
            </div>

            <h5><a href="/card/LL05-053/">LL05-053 "Mari Ohara"</a></h5>
            <div class="seealso">
                See also: <a href="/faq/general#join_success_order">What is the order
                    for <%- skillFormat("[Live Join]/[Live Success]") %> Skills?</a>
            </div>
            <div class="question" id="053">
                Can Pieces gained through <%- skillFormat("[Live Join]") %> Skills be used for this Skill's
                requirement?<br>
                For example, could <a href="/card/LL05-039/">LL05-039 "Kanan Matsuura"</a> be used as not only the
                Member for <%- skillFormat("[PURE], but also for [SMILE] or [COOL]") %> if her Skill is
                activated?
            </div>
            <div class="answer">
                Yes. If their requirements are met, Pieces gained through <%- skillFormat("[Live Join]") %>
                Skills can be used for this card's Skill's requirement.
            </div>

            <h5><a href="/card/LL05-054/">LL05-054 "Ruby Kurosawa"</a></h5>
            <div class="question" id="054">
                I <%- skillFormat("⟪ENTER⟫") %>ed this card through <a href="/card/LL04-054/">LL04-054 "Ruby
                    Kurosawa"</a>'s Skill. In that case, since <a href="/card/LL04-054/">LL04-054 "Ruby Kurosawa"</a> is
                placed at the bottom of the deck, can I <%- skillFormat("⟪ENTER⟫") %> it by choosing to show
                the bottom card of my deck with this card's Skill?
            </div>
            <div class="answer">
                Yes. <a href="/card/LL04-054/">LL04-054 "Ruby Kurosawa"</a> is at the bottom of the Deck at the time the
                <%- skillFormat("[Entry] Skill is resolved, so you can ⟪ENTER⟫") %> it from there.
            </div>

